1968;;Duffy;;British;;Robert Parrish;;James Coburn, James Mason, James Fox;;comedy/crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Duffy_(film);;Duffy is a cunning aristocrat of criminals who is hired by Stefane, a young playboy, to hijack a boat carrying several million dollars of his father's fortune. The plot succeeds, with a little help from Segolene, Stefane's girlfriend - but also with an unexpected, sudden turn of events.